date: COVID 19 UPDATE: Almost 140,000 people vaccinated in UK.Minister of Vaccines Nadhim Zahawi said that in England there were 108,000 vaccinations, in Scotland 18,000, in Wales 7,897 and in Northern Ireland 4,000, a total of 137,897 over seven days.breaknlinks.com
